p: Territory of Washington County of Walla Walla District Judge 1st Judicial District The United States of America To Judge Winegard Sheriff of Walla Walla County

Greeting You are hereby commanded to have the body of Edna Elenor Edwards otherwise Edna Elenor Montague because the John B. Montague the writ of Habeas Corpus Judge of the defendant of Washington Territory to the Walla Walla County Washington Territory the day of November at the hour of five oclock PM in the afternoon of that day to what shall then and there be awarded the said Edna Elenor Edwards otherwise Edna Elenor Montague this writ
Judge v of Washington Territory Court
